   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 532,
   "width": 1557.01,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Cloudflare and UniFi carry traffic to the Galaxy cluster, which hosts every platform. Each group below maps to its own guide: access publishing, the media stack, the security and monitoring stack, member services, and the automation and AI tooling.",
   "originalText": "Cloudflare and UniFi carry traffic to the Galaxy cluster, which hosts every platform. Each group below maps to its own guide: access publishing, the media stack, the security and monitoring stack, member services, and the automation and AI tooling.",
